snippet.title: Amber Heard May Get DC Mera Movie Following The Johnny Depp Case?
snippet.description:
I wanted to take a look at the future of Amber Heard's role in the DCEU and Aquaman 2. It has recently been revealed that she may also be getting her own film in the DC Universe. WB reportedly doesn't care about the petitions around Amber and doesn't believe people actually feel that way. I don't normally call for boycotts or tell people how to use their money but I did want to go over some things that you can do to make yourself heard. #justiceforjohnny #justiceforjohnnydepp #fantasticbeasts
